Summary: Green circle of light in the sky
trends: There have been 83 other sightings in Sacramento
There were no other sightings in Sacramento on or around November 12th 2008
divs: sighting detailsat about 7:30 p.m. on 11\12\08 i was outside my balcony and a green circle of light caught my eye. it looked like it was falling from the sky. my reaction was what the heck is this and then i wished i had had my camera. i only saw it for about 15 seconds as there is a church across the street from my balcony and i lost site of it behind the church. then on 11\13\08 at approximatley 8:45 a.m. i was listening to the radio and people were calling into the station saying they had seen the same thing.
